      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm a bit confused. you're saying that letting the ultra-wealthy keep more of their assets actually narrows the gap? that seems to contradict most economic models i've read. can you explain the logic behind how that works, and maybe cite which specific economic theory supports that conclusion?",
